headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid J and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since July 2025, Jacobs Solutions has been in a holding pattern, posting a small return of 3.4% while floating around $138.76. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 10.5% gain during that period.
